  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[The Example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>This is a simple registration&nbsp;<em>Form </em>that&nbsp;contains a set of input fields such as <em>TextBox</em>, <em>ComboBox </em>and <em>CheckBox</em>.<br />User has to fill all the fields and agree the terms to be successfully registered.<br />The <strong>'Register' </strong>button performs the validation. All fields with invalid values are highlighted with error icon.<br />The fields with valid values are highlighted with success icon as well.</p>]]></Paragraph>
